graph TB
    subgraph "vLLM Orchestrator Gateway"
        direction TB
        Main["main.rs<br/>Entry Point & Server Setup"]
        Config["config.rs<br/>YAML Config Loader"]
        API["api.rs<br/>OpenAI-Compatible Types"]
        TLSSetup["TLS Setup<br/>mTLS / PKCS#12 Identity"]

        Main -->|reads config| Config
        Main -->|uses types| API
        Main -->|configures| TLSSetup
    end

    subgraph "Dynamic Route Endpoints"
        Route1["POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>e.g., /pii/v1/chat/completions"]
        Route2["POST /passthrough/v1/chat/completions<br/>(no detectors)"]
    end

    Client[External Client] -->|POST 8090/TCP<br/>HTTP + Authorization header| Route1
    Client -->|POST 8090/TCP<br/>HTTP + Authorization header| Route2

    Route1 -->|injects detectors| Main
    Route2 -->|passthrough| Main

    subgraph "Config (YAML)"
        ConfigFile["config.yaml<br/>- orchestrator address<br/>- detector definitions<br/>- route→detector mappings<br/>- fallback messages"]
    end

    ConfigFile -.->|loaded at startup| Config

    subgraph "TLS Certificates"
        TLSCert["/etc/tls/private/tls.crt"]
        TLSKey["/etc/tls/private/tls.key"]
        CACert["/etc/tls/ca/service-ca.crt"]
    end

    TLSCert -.->|client cert| TLSSetup
    TLSKey -.->|private key| TLSSetup
    CACert -.->|CA trust| TLSSetup

    Main -->|POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>HTTP or HTTPS 8085/TCP<br/>Plaintext or mTLS| Orchestrator["FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator"]

    Orchestrator -->|calls| Detectors["Guardrails Detector<br/>Services<br/>(e.g., regex-language)"]
    Orchestrator -->|calls| vLLM["vLLM Inference<br/>Backend"]

    style Main fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style Config fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style API fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style TLSSetup fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style Route1 fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style Route2 fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style Orchestrator fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style Detectors fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style vLLM fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Client fill:#f9f9f9,stroke:#333
    style ConfigFile fill:#ddd,stroke:#333
    style TLSCert fill:#fff2cc,stroke:#d6b656
    style TLSKey fill:#fff2cc,stroke:#d6b656
    style CACert fill:#fff2cc,stroke:#d6b656
